---
import Button from '@/components/shared/Button.astro';
import classes from '@/data/styles.json';
---

<section class="bg-secondary-bg py-24 px-6 lg:px-12" id="about">
  <div class={classes.container}>
    <div class="flex flex-row gap-8">
      <div class="w-1/3">
        <h2 class={classes.heading}>
          Obsessed with <span class="text-gray-400">every detail.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class={classes.secondaryText}>
          I believe that the difference between good and great lies in the nuances. From the
          fluidity of an animation to the semantic structure of the DOM, I pour attention into every
          aspect of the frontend experience.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-4">
          <Button style="tertiary" href="#about-detail"> More about my process </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-2/3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div
          class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark border border-transparent hover:border-border-light dark:hover:border-border-dark transition-colors"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl mb-4 text-primary dark:text-white"
            >bolt</span
          >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Performance First</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Optimizing Core Web Vitals, code-splitting, and asset delivery to ensure instantaneous
            load times.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark border border-transparent hover:border-border-light dark:hover:border-border-dark transition-colors md:mt-12"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl mb-4 text-primary dark:text-white"
            >accessibility_new</span
          >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Inclusive Design</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Strict adherence to WCAG 2.1 guidelines ensuring the web is accessible to everyone,
            everywhere.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark border border-transparent hover:border-border-light dark:hover:border-border-dark transition-colors"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl mb-4 text-primary dark:text-white"
            >grid_view</span
          >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Pixel Perfect</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Translating Figma designs into responsive code with exact precision and fluid
            responsiveness.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark border border-transparent hover:border-border-light dark:hover:border-border-dark transition-colors md:mt-12"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl mb-4 text-primary dark:text-white"
            >integration_instructions</span
          >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Type Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Leveraging TypeScript to build robust, scalable applications with fewer runtime errors.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
